# text: And then she did very well for many years on lithium , and then eventually , she was taken off her lithium to see how she would do without it , and she had another psychosis , and then plunged into the worst depression that I had ever seen in which she sat in her parents ' apartment , more or less catatonic , essentially without moving , day after day after day .
