# text: I went through a tribal exorcism in Senegal that involved a great deal of ram 's blood and that I 'm not going to detail right now , but a few years afterwards I was in Rwanda , working on a different project , and I happened to describe my experience to someone , and he said , `` Well , that 's West Africa , and we 're in East Africa , and our rituals are in some ways very different , but we do have some rituals that have something in common with what you 're describing . ''
